## 📐 代码质量规范

### 1. 函数单一职责

```javascript
// ❌ 不好：一个函数做多件事
function handlePhotoUpload(photo) {
  validatePhoto(photo);
  compressPhoto(photo);
  uploadPhoto(photo);
  updateUI();
  showNotification();
}

// ✅ 好：拆分为多个单一职责函数
async function uploadPhoto(photo) {
  const validated = validatePhoto(photo);
  const compressed = await compressPhoto(validated);
  const result = await sendToServer(compressed);
  return result;
}

function updateUIAfterUpload(result) {
  refreshPhotoList();
  showSuccessMessage(result);
}
```

### 2. 避免嵌套过深

```javascript
// ❌ 不好：嵌套过深
function processData(data) {
  if (data) {
    if (data.photos) {
      if (data.photos.length > 0) {
        data.photos.forEach((photo) => {
          if (photo.url) {
            // 处理逻辑
          }
        });
      }
    }
  }
}

// ✅ 好：提前返回，降低嵌套
function processData(data) {
  if (!data?.photos?.length) return;

  data.photos
    .filter((photo) => photo.url)
    .forEach((photo) => {
      // 处理逻辑
    });
}
```

### 3. 简洁明了

```javascript
// ❌ 不好：冗长复杂
function checkPermission(user) {
  let hasPermission = false;
  if (user !== null && user !== undefined) {
    if (user.role === "admin" || user.role === "moderator") {
      hasPermission = true;
    }
  }
  return hasPermission;
}

// ✅ 好：简洁清晰
function checkPermission(user) {
  return ["admin", "moderator"].includes(user?.role);
}
```

### 4. UI 还原标准

- **1:1 还原**：严格按照设计图实现，像素级对齐
- **响应式优先**：移动端和桌面端都要完美适配
- **交互细节**：悬停效果、过渡动画、加载状态等不可遗漏

